Class FakeRDotTxtEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.android.aapt.RDotTxtEntry
      • com.facebook.buck.android.aapt.FakeRDotTxtEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<RDotTxtEntry>

    public class FakeRDotTxtEntry
extends RDotTxtEntry
    An RDotTxtEntry with fake RDotTxtEntry.idValue, useful for comparing two resource entries for equality, since RDotTxtEntry.compareTo(RDotTxtEntry) ignores the id value.
